wiki.summary: "I'm Unhappy" is a song recorded by South Korean girl group aespa, released on May 8, 2023 along with its mini album, 'MY WORLD', being the fifth track for it. It's a charming, bedroom-pop genre song, a minimal track paired with dreamy and chic vocals. It was performed for the first time at aespa's first concert on February 25, 2023. During the 'MY WORLD' promotions, a track video for the song was released on May 3rd. Read more on Last.fm.
